<!DOCTYPE html>
<!-- saved from url=(0132)blob:https://443sqqbrztv1wgkivbnq7t86wo7iowht2yriuz11b1jfixn9gk-h936707426.scf.usercontent.goog/838301d5-6299-45e4-b65a-01525c8753d8 -->
<html lang="en"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>26 Ara Ville | Exclusivity &amp; Style</title>
    <style>
        /* Font Definitions */
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'yaezxhw1plk-0';
            src: url('https://labs.google.com/pomelli_downloads/websites/b6oxFEut0FudOmihZT7kqS/resources/aEpz5o6pVHnaaBnF-OxOJk?authuser=0') format('woff2'),
                 url('https://labs.google.com/pomelli_downloads/websites/b6oxFEut0FudOmihZT7kqS/resources/aEpz5o6pVHnaaBnF-OxOJk?authuser=0') format('woff');
            font-weight: normal;
            font-style: normal;
            font-display: swap;
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'yad1au3slni-0';
            src: url('https://labs.google.com/pomelli_downloads/websites/b6oxFEut0FudOmihZT7kqS/resources/9Fls5-4x-QIbxC9srIWOOd?authuser=0') format('woff2'),
                 url('https://labs.google.com/pomelli_downloads/websites/b6oxFEut0FudOmihZT7kqS/resources/9Fls5-4x-QIbxC9srIWOOd?authuser=0') format('woff');
            font-weight: normal;
            font-style: normal;
            font-display: swap;
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'yafdjqkjit4-0';
            src: url('https://labs.google.com/pomelli_downloads/websites/b6oxFEut0FudOmihZT7kqS/resources/8uAViG-EJNO2SFp7wqjk-T?authuser=0') format('woff2'),
                 url('https://labs.google.com/pomelli_downloads/websites/b6oxFEut0FudOmihZT7kqS/resources/8uAViG-EJNO2SFp7wqjk-T?authuser=0') format('woff');
            font-weight: normal;
            font-style: normal;
            font-display: swap;
        }

        /* Variables */
        :root {
            --col-cream: #efebe5;
            --col-brown: #623e2a;
            --col-white: #ffffff;
            --col-text: #2a2a2a;
            --col-accent: #8b6045;
            
            --font-primary: 'yaezxhw1plk-0', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
            --font-heading: 'yad1au3slni-0', 'yaezxhw1plk-0', serif;
            
            --header-height: 90px;
            --section-pad: 8rem;
        }

        /* Reset & Base */
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
            scroll-padding-top: var(--header-height);
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        body {
            font-family: var(--font-primary);
            color: var(--col-text);
            background-color: var(--col-white);
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding-top: var(--header-height);
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        /* Typography */
        h1, h2, h3, h4 {
            font-family: var(--font-heading);
            color: var(--col-brown);
            font-weight: normal;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
            letter-spacing: -0.01em;
        }
        h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #4a4a4a;
        }
        .eyebrow {
            display: block;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--col-accent);
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Utilities */
        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: var(--section-pad) 2rem;
        }
        .bg-light {
            background-color: var(--col-cream);
        }
        .bg-white {
            background-color: var(--col-white);
        }
        
        /* Image Watermark Safety Rules */
        img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
        }
        .img-cover {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            object-position: bottom right; /* Ensures bottom right watermark is never cropped */
        }
        .bg-cover {
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: bottom right; /* Ensures bottom right watermark is never cropped */
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: var(--header-height);
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            z-index: 300;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(98, 62, 42, 0.1);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .header-inner {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
        }
        .logo img {
            height: 48px;
            width: auto;
            mix-blend-mode: darken; /* Removes white bg from logo */
        }
        nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2.5rem;
        }
        nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--col-brown);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            position: relative;
            padding: 0.5rem 0;
        }
        nav a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 1px;
            background-color: var(--col-brown);
            transform: scaleX(0);
            transform-origin: right;
            transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
        }
        nav a:hover::after {
            transform: scaleX(1);
            transform-origin: left;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.75rem;
            background-color: var(--col-brown);
            color: var(--col-white);
            text-decoration: none;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: var(--col-accent);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        #hero {
            position: relative;
            height: calc(100vh - var(--header-height));
            min-height: 600px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .hero-bg {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .hero-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--col-white) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85) 40%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 100%);
            z-index: 2;
        }
        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 3;
            max-width: 650px;
            animation: slideUpFade 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
        }
        @keyframes slideUpFade {
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* Split Layout */
        .split-layout {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 6rem;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .image-wrapper {
            position: relative;
        }
        .image-wrapper::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -2rem;
            left: 2rem;
            right: -2rem;
            bottom: 2rem;
            background-color: var(--col-brown);
            opacity: 0.05;
            z-index: -1;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }
        .image-wrapper:hover::before {
            transform: translate(-1rem, 1rem);
        }
        .image-wrapper img {
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
        }

        /* Lifestyle / Products Grid */
        .section-header {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 5rem auto;
        }
        .grid-2 {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
            gap: 4rem;
        }
        .feature-card {
            background-color: var(--col-white);
            padding: 3rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(98, 62, 42, 0.08);
            transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease;
        }
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(98, 62, 42, 0.08);
        }
        .feature-img-box {
            height: 350px;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            background-color: var(--col-cream);
        }

        /* Gallery */
        .gallery-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
            gap: 2rem;
        }
        .gallery-item {
            position: relative;
        }
        .gallery-item:nth-child(1) { grid-column: span 12; height: 600px; }
        .gallery-item:nth-child(2) { grid-column: span 7; height: 450px; }
        .gallery-item:nth-child(3) { grid-column: span 5; height: 450px; }
        
        .gallery-item::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
            background-color: var(--col-brown);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .gallery-item:hover::after {
            opacity: 0.1;
        }

        /* Masterplan */
        .plan-box {
            background-color: var(--col-white);
            padding: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: var(--col-white);
            padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(98, 62, 42, 0.1);
        }
        .footer-inner {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer-logo {
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }
        .footer-logo img {
            height: 60px;
            mix-blend-mode: darken;
        }
        .footer-legal {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            color: #888;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            :root {
                --section-pad: 5rem;
            }
            .split-layout {
                gap: 3rem;
            }
            .gallery-item:nth-child(1),
            .gallery-item:nth-child(2),
            .gallery-item:nth-child(3) {
                grid-column: span 12;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header {
                position: static;
                height: auto;
                padding: 1rem 0;
            }
            body {
                padding-top: 0;
            }
            .header-inner {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1.5rem;
            }
            nav {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                justify-content: center;
                gap: 1.5rem;
            }
            .split-layout {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .split-layout .text-content {
                order: 2;
            }
            .split-layout .image-wrapper {
                order: 1;
            }
            .image-wrapper::before {
                display: none;
            }
            #hero {
                min-height: auto;
                padding: 6rem 0;
                height: auto;
            }
            .hero-overlay {
                background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255,255,255,0.9) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.7) 100%);
            }
            .grid-2 {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="header-inner">
            <a href="blob:https://443sqqbrztv1wgkivbnq7t86wo7iowht2yriuz11b1jfixn9gk-h936707426.scf.usercontent.goog/838301d5-6299-45e4-b65a-01525c8753d8#" class="logo">
                <img src="https://labs.google.com/pomelli_downloads/websites/b6oxFEut0FudOmihZT7kqS/resources/9fGxb8jz30S5h_lVpnekHo?authuser=0" alt="26 Ara Ville Logo">
            </a>
            <nav>
                <a href="blob:https://443sqqbrztv1wgkivbnq7t86wo7iowht2yriuz11b1jfixn9gk-h936707426.scf.usercontent.goog/838301d5-6299-45e4-b65a-01525c8753d8#concept">The Concept</a>
                <a href="blob:https://443sqqbrztv1wgkivbnq7t86wo7iowht2yriuz11b1jfixn9gk-h936707426.scf.usercontent.goog/838301d5-6299-45e4-b65a-01525c8753d8#lifestyle">Lifestyle</a>
                <a href="blob:https://443sqqbrztv1wgkivbnq7t86wo7iowht2yriuz11b1jfixn9gk-h936707426.scf.usercontent.goog/838301d5-6299-45e4-b65a-01525c8753d8#gallery">Gallery</a>
                <a href="blob:https://443sqqbrztv1wgkivbnq7t86wo7iowht2yriuz11b1jfixn9gk-h936707426.scf.usercontent.goog/838301d5-6299-45e4-b65a-01525c8753d8#masterplan">Masterplan</a>
            </nav>
            <a href="https://wa.link/6qxn2f" class="cta-button" target="_blank">Inquire Now</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section id="hero">
        <div class="hero-bg bg-cover" style="background-image: url(&#39;https://labs.google.com/pomelli_downloads/websites/b6oxFEut0FudOmihZT7kqS/resources/bnnSrYzXifJfZsyfu8a_MV?authuser=0&#39;);"></div>
        <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
        <div class="container hero-content">
            <h1>Welcome Home to Exclusivity &amp; Style</h1>
            <p>An exclusive gated and guarded residential community offering luxury three-story homes designed for the discerning few.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="concept" class="bg-light">
        <div class="container split-layout">
            <div class="text-content">
                <span class="eyebrow">Quiet Luxury</span>
                <h2>A Sanctuary of Minimalist Elegance</h2>
                <p>26 Ara Ville is an exclusive gated and guarded residential community offering luxury three-story homes designed for the discerning few. The development features exactly 26 units that seamlessly blend sleek modern minimalism with the surrounding nature.</p>
                <p>We provide spacious, highly functional living environments curated specifically for families seeking absolute privacy and uncompromising style.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="image-wrapper">
                <img src="https://labs.google.com/pomelli_downloads/websites/b6oxFEut0FudOmihZT7kqS/resources/9-AUOPmKT2vb-c0nzYNk7u?authuser=0" alt="Modern residential courtyard framed by sleek white and charcoal-grey buildings with vertical wooden slat accents" class="img-cover">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="lifestyle" class="bg-white">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span class="eyebrow">The Experience</span>
                <h2>Curated Living Environments</h2>
                <p>Positioned as an ultra-exclusive residential enclave, our focus remains squarely on delivering a high-status lifestyle integrated seamlessly with practical design.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid-2">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-img-box">
                        <div class="bg-cover" style="background-image: url(&#39;https://labs.google.com/pomelli_downloads/websites/b6oxFEut0FudOmihZT7kqS/resources/aTksN2R2QSM4i5G-7f9k53?authuser=0&#39;); height: 100%;" data-alt="Close up of a solid, heavy brushed bronze gate latch and handle against a dark slatted wood surface, soft warm lighting highlighting the metallic texture and conveying a feeling of exclusivity and security. Minimalist and refined. No text, signage, or lettering."></div>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Gated &amp; Guarded Privacy</h3>
                    <p>Providing a highly secure living environment within an exclusive gated community, ensuring absolute privacy and safety for all residents through controlled access and dedicated security services.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-img-box">
                        <img src="https://labs.google.com/pomelli_downloads/websites/b6oxFEut0FudOmihZT7kqS/resources/bfGMLBxa45N99xsBDHaOa_?authuser=0" alt="Luxurious modern open-plan living and dining space with high-end furniture and geometric chandelier" class="img-cover">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Luxury Residential Development</h3>
                    <p>The careful development of exclusive, luxury residential properties that perfectly blend modern minimalistic design with practical, generous living spaces and natural, biophilic surroundings.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="gallery" class="bg-light">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span class="eyebrow">Visual Tour</span>
                <h2>Architectural Brilliance</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="gallery-grid">
                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <img src="https://labs.google.com/pomelli_downloads/websites/b6oxFEut0FudOmihZT7kqS/resources/8kz0eMkIYKw1i4nK_eokwX?authuser=0" alt="Contemporary two-story residential building with a sleek, minimalist white and gray facade" class="img-cover">
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <img src="https://labs.google.com/pomelli_downloads/websites/b6oxFEut0FudOmihZT7kqS/resources/85NCEoPx3Mf4ml6FMdHktO?authuser=0" alt="Modern outdoor patio furnished with a set of woven sofas and framed by manicured hedges" class="img-cover">
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <img src="https://labs.google.com/pomelli_downloads/websites/b6oxFEut0FudOmihZT7kqS/resources/bVcQL799MG33LEwo6Tz_X7?authuser=0" alt="Row of contemporary multi-story residential buildings characterized by minimalist facades" class="img-cover">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="masterplan" class="bg-white">
        <div class="container split-layout">
            <div class="plan-box">
                <img src="https://labs.google.com/pomelli_downloads/websites/b6oxFEut0FudOmihZT7kqS/resources/bgMl67qkAtOeITQNiqFOrZ?authuser=0" alt="2D architectural site plan of the residential development featuring four building blocks" class="img-cover" style="object-fit: contain;">
            </div>
            <div class="text-content">
                <span class="eyebrow">The Blueprint</span>
                <h2>Thoughtful Exclusivity</h2>
                <p>Designed for discerning families who value peer cultural proof and an ultra-exclusive market presence, the masterplan of 26 Ara Ville reflects a modern trend-led approach.</p>
                <p>The layout is intentionally low-density, organized around central landscaped areas to maximize natural light, privacy, and community flow.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-inner">
            <div class="footer-logo">
                <img src="https://labs.google.com/pomelli_downloads/websites/b6oxFEut0FudOmihZT7kqS/resources/9fGxb8jz30S5h_lVpnekHo?authuser=0" alt="26 Ara Ville Logo">
            </div>
            <div class="footer-legal">
                © 26 Ara Ville. All rights reserved.
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

